{"lemma":"فُرْصَةُ","slug":"فُرْصَةُ","root":"ف.ر.ص","root_slug":"ف-ر-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ر-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33549","n33557","n33558","n33559"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chance, occasion, opportunity","examples":[{"text":"اِسْتَغِل الْفُرْصَةَ عِنْدَمَا تَأْتِي، فَقَدْ لَا تَعُودُ مَرَّةً أُخْرَى.","english":"Seize the opportunity when it comes; it may not come again."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a rag to wipe the catamenia, pad"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"While it would be tempting to connect to the root ف ر ص (f r ṣ) related to slitting, being the timespan in which one’s camels have access to a body of water shared with other herders, Aramaic פורסא / ܦܘܪܣܐ (pursā, “way out, knack, strategy, scheme”), from Ancient Greek πόρος (póros), acknowledging its pervasive colloquial use, should be believed to have developed its semantics to a “chance, opportunity, occasion” as well and therefore served as the source of the present Arabic term.\n\nFrom فَرَصَ (faraṣa, “to slit up”)."},"ipa":["/fur.sˤa/","/fir.sˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33549","headword_ar":"فَرَصَهُ","root":"frS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frs","text_ar":"فرس"},{"kind":"text","text":",) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroSN","text_ar":"فَرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) namely, skin, or a skin, (M,) [and metal; (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miforaSN","text_ar":"مِفْرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)] or it signifies, (TA,) or signifies also, (S, K,) sometimes, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he slit it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided it lengthwise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made a hole in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) namely, skin, or a skin: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he slit it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a skin,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with an iron instrument having a wide end, like as the maker of sandals slits the two ears of the sandal at the heel, to put into them the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAk","text_ar":"شِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two arms of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rAk","text_ar":"شراك"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lth, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraSotu Aln~aEola","text_ar":"فَرَصْتُ النَّعْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made a hole in each of the two ears of the sandal, for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rAk","text_ar":"شراك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the two arms of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rAk","text_ar":"شراك"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A2-  Also, (S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [so in a copy of the M, but accord. to a rule of the K it should rather be"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n. as above, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt, his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariySap","text_ar":"فَرِيصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; (M, K; and so in a copy of the S;) or, accord. to [other copies of] the S,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariyS","text_ar":"فَرِيص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; (TA;) which is a place where a wound causes death. (S.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariSa","text_ar":"فَرِصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraSN","text_ar":"فَرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furiSa","text_ar":"فُرِصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroSN","text_ar":"فَرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had a complaint of his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariySap","text_ar":"فَرِيصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraSa AlfuroSapa","text_ar":"فَرَصَ الفُرْصَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8."}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","S","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n33557","headword_ar":"فَرْصَةٌ","root":"frS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoSapN","text_ar":"فِرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaroSapu","text_ar":"الفَرْصَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyH","text_ar":"رِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flatus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which results gibbosity"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the back"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHadabu","text_ar":"الحَدَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (S, M, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfarosapu","text_ar":"الفَرْسَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof: (M, TA:) or, accord. to A 'Obeyd, the latter [q. v.] is vulgar. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n33558","headword_ar":"فُرْصَةٌ","root":"frS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turn; a time at which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during which, a thing is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is to be, done,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had, in succession:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a turn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time, for"},{"kind":"text","text":"persons'"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming to water in succession,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yaakoob, S, * M, A, * Msb, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the cases of the periodical drinkings of their camels, such as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximos","text_ar":"خِمْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riboE","text_ar":"رِبْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidos","text_ar":"سِدْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yaakoob, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the water is little;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoSapN","text_ar":"فِرْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariySapN","text_ar":"فَرِيصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Yaakoob, M:) a dial. var. of the same is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar, M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufoSapN","text_ar":"رُفْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is another: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furaSN","text_ar":"فُرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='ato furoSatuka mina Albiy^ori","text_ar":"جَا=ءَتْ فُرْصَتُكَ مِنَ البِيْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy turn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time, for watering from the well has come."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, * Msb. *) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"share, of what falls to one's lot, of water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irobN","text_ar":"شِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An opportunity; a time at which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during which, a thing may be done,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhozapN","text_ar":"نُهْزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furosapN","text_ar":"فُرْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. of the same. (M.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ainotahaza","text_ar":"اِنْتَهَزَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfuroSapa","text_ar":"الفُرْصَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AigotanamahaA","text_ar":"اِغْتَنَمَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. above: see 8]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmuka furaSN","text_ar":"اَيَّامُكَ فُرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy days are opportunities"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoSapN","text_ar":"فِرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"temper"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sajiy~ap","text_ar":"سَجِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outstripping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n33559","headword_ar":"فِرْصَةٌ","root":"frS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of wool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of cotton,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, M, O, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of rag,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which a woman wipes herself, to purify herself from the catamenia;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, * O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroSapN","text_ar":"فَرْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furoSapN","text_ar":"فُرْصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Kr, M:) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraSa","text_ar":"فَرَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning “ he cut ” a thing: (As, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaASN","text_ar":"فِرَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaASN","text_ar":"فِرَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoSapN","text_ar":"فِرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, O.) ―         -b2-  And, accord. to AAF,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bit, of mush."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"furoSapN","text_ar":"فُرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["As","M","S","O","Msb","K","Kr","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}